                  <h5 class="card-title">Happy Hunters for Enterprises</h5>
                  <p class="card-text margintop20">Happy Hunters lets you engage or source top developers with hackathons, while also enabling you to assess, interview and upskill them with ease. </p>
                  <a href="/recruiter/login" class="btn btn-primary">Hire now</a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6">
              <div class="card">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title">Happy Hunters for Developers</h5>
                  <p class="card-text margintop20">Happy Hunters lets you showcase your coding skills, appear for interviews and find your next dream job easily with over 500+ companies. Find a job now.
                 </p>
                  <a href="/candidate/login" class="btn btn-primary">Apply now</a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>          
    </div>
    
    
